{"tid":189923,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"攝影師原想拉近拍攝月亮，拉近看才知是快餐店標誌","createTime":"2017-04-06T18:47:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-07T08:41:15.000Z","uid":36073,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"42f5f3fd2b72cec35a550ef2f42ce484d180d7bb","tid":189923,"uid":36073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T18:47:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2017/04/hownottophotographthemoonfeat-800x420.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetapixel.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F04%2Fhownottophotographthemoonfeat-800x420.jpg&h=86b1677f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國華盛頓一位攝影記者 Van Applegate，在馬利蘭洲一個小鎮拍攝片段。他在拍攝時，剛好圓月升至遠處一棵樹裡，形成了一個漂亮畫面。那刻他決定要拉近拍攝那棵樹，記錄月光穿透樹枝的美景。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2017/04/originalshot-800x450.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetapixel.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F04%2Foriginalshot-800x450.jpg&h=54fa544e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但看來有點不對。他向PetaPixel記者說：「我已感覺到它不是月亮...」<br />\n<br />\n他再說：「拉近後對焦更明顯。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2017/04/C79pGyVWkAAmKFt-800x450.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetapixel.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F04%2FC79pGyVWkAAmKFt-800x450.jpg&h=c2245984&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2017/04/C79pGy2X0AAjQtw-800x450.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetapixel.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F04%2FC79pGy2X0AAjQtw-800x450.jpg&h=54b46734&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n看來攝影師所望見的「月亮」，一直是漢堡王標誌的燈箱偽裝。他說笑：「典型錯誤。」<br />\n<br />\n事後他把這「美麗的誤會」分享至Twitter，還給網民瘋傳。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pMFo3K2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpMFo3K2.png&h=3c747e59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「好像很多人都明白是怎麼一回事，但只有我這個笨蛋會分享在網上。」<br />\n<br />\n這回事更引起漢堡王的注意，在Twitter上留言想得他同意下轉載至官方粉絲頁。攝影師作笑回了一句：「一生享用華堡嗎？」<br />\n<img src=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2017/04/burgerkingtweet.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetapixel.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F04%2Fburgerkingtweet.jpg&h=e3058296&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然這「月亮」是一場美麗的誤會，但令攝影記者 Van Applegate擁有突如其來的名氣，他也要在Twitter的個人介紹中炫耀一下。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2017/04/twitterbio-800x473.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetapixel.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F04%2Ftwitterbio-800x473.jpg&h=dbb99219&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原文: <a href=\"https://petapixel.com/2017/04/06/not-photograph-moon/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetapixel.com%2F2017%2F04%2F06%2Fnot-photograph-moon%2F&d=dKvfM97HALqNkq2vb6iplKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=04e10bca\" target=\"_blank\">https://petapixel.com/2017/04/06/not-photograph-moon/</a>"},{"pid":"e7f43ebf24d383ac5ca239197d44d8fd58d8ff18","tid":189923,"uid":30794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T18:53:45.000Z","msg":"又真係幾似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bc98cf1b51a7a75ea8dde3bb7c321d02e9eaba2","tid":189923,"uid":36073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T18:55:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"613989ae80c8b4d2b98533273fc21b515ec2a88f","tid":189923,"uid":56729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T19:13:08.000Z","msg":"錯有錯著 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f60789b93826a29f544aa48a85651777063c550c","tid":189923,"uid":33053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T19:16:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dafcb6724b3c34d6ecd46fc27fc1f9bf77d3de71","tid":189923,"uid":1152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit